testcase.title: Check that filters are returned by default and verify default value for hits and offset

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "REST" API
I pass a "query = cancer" as parameter to "getLiteratureStructureResultsV2" operation
I call poll async "180" times with interval "1" seconds I should get the response
I get a response with "20" integer values in tag "hits"
I get a response with "0" integer values in tag "offset"
response contains "filters" in fields.
